definitions: The fifth letter of the alphabet.
Denoting the fifth in a set of items, categories, sizes, etc.
The fifth-highest class of academic mark.
Denoting the fifth file from the left, as viewed from White's side of the board.
Denoting the lowest-earning socio-economic category for marketing purposes.
A shape like that of a capital E.
The third note of the diatonic scale of C major.
A key based on a scale with E as its keynote.
